headline: Is Phillips 66 (PSX) Still Attractively Priced After Strong Multi‑Year Share Gains
summary: If you are wondering whether Phillips 66 at around US$138 per share still offers value, or if the easy gains are behind it, this article walks through what the current price might really be telling you. The stock has had a mixed short term patch, with a 2.7% decline over the last 7 days, a 7.3% gain over 30 days, a 5.9% return year to date, and a 19.0% return over the last year. The 3 year and 5 year returns sit at 44.1% and 131.7% respectively. These moves have played out against an ongoing...
